    "section-rich-text-data": {
      "type": "section-rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Our Data Protection Approach",
            "heading_font_size": "heading-medium",
            "padding_bottom": 16,
            "heading_tag": "automatic"
          }
        },
        "text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Role-Based Access Control</strong></p><p>Your information is compartmentalized. Only clinicians who need clinical information can access it. Your billing information is separate from your medical records. Administrative staff can only see what's necessary for their role.</p><p><strong>Comprehensive Audit Trail</strong></p><p>Every access to your information is logged. If you want to know who viewed your records, we can tell you. Our system tracks all data access for complete accountability.</p><p><strong>Rapid Breach Response</strong></p><p>If a security incident occurs, we notify you and regulators within 72 hours (as required by PIPEDA) and provide guidance on protecting yourself. We maintain detailed procedures for all jurisdictions.</p>",
            "text_font_size": "body-medium",
            "padding_bottom": 24
          }
        }
      },
